  <chapter>
    <title>CTPL overview</title>
    <para>
      CTPL is a template library written in C.
    </para>
    <para>
      CTPL depends on the following libraries:
      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term><ulink url="http://www.gtk.org">GLib</ulink></term>
          <listitem>
            <para>
              General purpose C utility library
            </para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term><ulink url="http://ban.free-h.net/libmb/">LibMB</ulink></term>
          <listitem>
            <para>
              FILE-like API for memory buffer read
            </para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </para>
  </chapter>

